commentPostTextItems.html: Kenya were well beaten here again today, A thigh muscle injury for Odoyo prevented him from batting not and Kamande has a recurrent leg ankle injury and was run out struggling to get there, but credit to Zimbabwe for outplaying Kenya in all departments
